// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0075 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 091edd92-6b9e-5837-964e-21e31771ee07

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*cbl-mariner:2.0*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
